print("Pisces")
</code></pre> Autori ProblemPython <p>See detail at https://open.kattis.com/problems/autori.</p> <pre><code>print("".join([part[0] for part in input().split("-")]))
</code></pre> Average Character ProblemPython <p>See detail at https://open.kattis.com/problems/averagecharacter.</p> <pre><code>s = input()
