record[item] = [name]
else:
record[item].append(name)
for name in sorted(record):
print(name, " ".join(sorted(record[name])))
print()
</code></pre> Basketball One-on-One ProblemJavaPython <p>See detail at https://open.kattis.com/problems/basketballoneonone.</p> <pre><code>import java.util.Scanner;
